OL,3,CNew anti-spiking technology introduced
OL,4,Cto tackle vape tampering
OL,6,FNew vape-spiking detection equipment
OL,7,Fis being deployed across London as
OL,8,Fpart of a major police crackdown,
OL,9,Ftargeting bars, clubs, and even party
OL,10,Fboats.
OL,12,FChildren as young as 14 were admitted
OL,13,Fto hospital after cannabis products
OL,14,Fwere placed in vapes in a case in
OL,15,Fsouth-east London, according to the
OL,16,FMetropolitan Police.
