OL,3,CNew anti-spiking technology introduced
OL,4,Cto tackle vape tampering
OL,6,FThe cutting-edge technology, already
OL,7,Fused at nightclubs, festivals,
OL,8,Fconcerts, and schools, can quickly
OL,9,Ftest for substances like THC or spice,
OL,10,Fthe force claims.
