OL,3,CNew anti-spiking technology introduced
OL,4,Cto tackle vape tampering
OL,6,FMobile drug-testing tools are also
OL,7,Fbeing used in schools, including near
OL,8,Finfra-red detectors for identifying
OL,9,Fpowders and tablets - technology
OL,10,Fsupported by a mobile app for rapid
OL,11,Fanalysis.
OL,13,FBetween March 2024 and March 2025,
OL,14,Fover 2,000 spiking incidents were
OL,15,Freported to the Met.
OL,17,FBut police believe the real number is
OL,18,Flikely much higher due to under-
OL,19,Freporting.
