OL,3,CNew anti-spiking technology introduced
OL,4,Cto tackle vape tampering
OL,6,FThe majority of victims are women and
OL,7,Fgirls - 66% in August 2025 were female
OL,8,F- with hotspots around Westminster and
OL,9,Fthe West End.
OL,11,FHome Office minister Jess Phillips
OL,12,Fsaid more must be done to protect
OL,13,Fyoung people during events like
OL,14,FFreshers Week.
OL,16,F"We are determined to tackle the vile
OL,17,Fcrime of spiking," she said.
